1. *Odlazimo* večeras u grad. (We are leaving for the city tonight.)

2. Svi *odlazimo* u istom smjeru. (We are all leaving in the same direction.)

3. *Odlazim* kod prijatelja. (I am leaving to visit a friend.)

4. Da li *odlazite* sa nama? (Are you leaving with us?)

5. Zbogom, *odlazimo*! (Goodbye, we are leaving!)

6. Oni su već *odlazili*. (They already left.)

7. Šta *odlazimo* da radimo? (What are we leaving to do?)